# Artifact content is transient — ignore everything
*

# But keep directory structure via .gitkeep
!.gitignore
!*/
!**/.gitkeep

# ADRs are stable architectural decisions — always committed
!decisions/*.md

# Completed design docs are committed for auditability
!designs/completed/*.md

# Archived design docs persist after clearing completed/
!designs/archive/
!designs/archive/*.md

# Keep plan examples committed
!plans/examples/
!plans/examples/*.md
